data.description: Your next home is nestled in the Gatewood Addition of Lakepoint. Just south of the Wichita Country club with only a few entrances to the neighborhood. This gorgeous home has 5 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms and is just shy of 4,200 square feet. The double door entrance welcomes you into a foyer, with a staircase to the second level. The den to the left could be a great home office or extra living space. The formal dining room is conveniently located across the foyer and near the kitchen. The main level boasts a large living room with a fireplace, vaulted ceiling and wet bar access from the kitchen area. There is also a bedroom and main level bathroom accessible from the living room. The kitchen has an island, desk and eating space. The eating space in the kitchen has a patio door that allows an abundance of natural light. The countertops are granite, and the kitchen sink is located below a window facing the backyard. The laundry room is located on the main floor near the kitchen. The main bedroom is located on the upper floor with a large master bathroom with a walk-in tile shower, double vanities, and walk in closet. Down the hall are 2 more spacious bedrooms, and another full bathroom. The basement offers more living space with a family room with an egress window, a very large bonus room, the 5th bedroom, and another full bathroom. There is a 3-car garage and plenty of driveway space. The lakes are the best part of the neighborhood. The lakes are open for all homeowners to enjoy. There is a wide, lighted, walking/jogging path along the lakes. Combined with the close-to-town location and the appeal of the wooded surroundings makes this property a must have. Book your private showing today.
